{"tid":991692,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【一人一個】單戀暗戀時會做既瘋狂野","createTime":"2019-01-22T14:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T08:00:34.000Z","uid":67045,"like":167,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"172d8e806ec415201996a2eac16dffdff8f59988","tid":991692,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"1. 睇哂IG所有post, 分析埋最常like及留言既acc, 從而推斷該人與目標對象既關係<br />\n<br />\n2. 臨訓前幻想各種與目標對象既親密行為<br />\n<br />\n3. 會瘋狂check whatsapp/fb online 時間，從而推斷目標對象既生活作息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 每次與目標對象text交流，情緒都會大喜大悲：<br />\n&mdash;藍剔為大悲；<br />\n&mdash;對方回覆幾個msg為大喜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51d74514ab88d669579988dfcdc45a8ff5289b6","tid":991692,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78c6c6aad6da09b55ba75271d9ec7a42605ea8b2","tid":991692,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"叫春"},{"pid":"df8ee061b75e7e5967367d29af10e01fdc6b1967","tid":991692,"uid":126255,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"On whatsapp係為咗睇佢last seen<br />\n撞正佢online會望到佢off為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da49725401160ae521d4485996b1bc3443db71a","tid":991692,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"進階版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當目標對象係男/女神或有知名度人士時：<br />\n<br />\n*1. 會瘋狂Google Search各大新聞/媒體/YouTube 去搜尋目標對象蹤影，然後將所得資訊用簿寫低<br />\n<br />\n*2. 會收集一切與目標對象有關既報導/雜誌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n*3. 養成cross-check 資料既習慣，從各大媒體不同的報導中交叉比對、辨證資訊真偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf0e8f2e22fad119f54a9303783189cb159dca5","tid":991692,"uid":67045,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"df8ee061b75e7e5967367d29af10e01fdc6b1967","tid":991692,"uid":126255,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"On whatsapp係為咗睇佢last seen<br />\n撞正佢online會望到佢off為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"5. 一遇上目標對象online, 會瘋狂FF對方其實係text自己，然後大腦高速轉動諗應該如何回覆，但其實對方根本完全沒有text你的打算"},{"pid":"d291ebd9c0c12f95a8c35f9290ec30773e7d18e8","tid":991692,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"死變態"},{"pid":"bf85cd0e20aacef8c84806b776a603d628eb07ed","tid":991692,"uid":229408,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"不斷聽果首當日認識佢而鍾意左既歌<br />\n一播就諗起佢<br />\n單曲循環可以一個月播左百幾次<br />\n每日返工放工都聽<br />\n懷疑緊自己係咪有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d636ba46b353ad60bc2287cce65d592f032204","tid":991692,"uid":116071,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"好想見到佢online<br />\n但見到佢online又唔係text自己 又會心諗佢究竟同邊個text緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac7286c1ad629ee7c79656896864fdbda427c5a","tid":991692,"uid":210161,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"讀書個陣<br />\n<br />\n每日行去接佢返學放學<br />\n連埋行去佢屋企段路 都每日行左兩個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n隨傳隨到<br />\n考試前一日都同佢出街9 hea<br />\n<br />\n自己慳埋所有錢都拎黎買野比佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當兵六年"},{"pid":"a586e6ba48fd3530b2f5f578f8f5a77d0b578233","tid":991692,"uid":231980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f51d74514ab88d669579988dfcdc45a8ff5289b6","tid":991692,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"好變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1b7cfd96e4093c08f1e9eb7252169a7fe9e11e","tid":991692,"uid":171119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b1eb01c36c7927a60b5a41070f119147c9f6d3","tid":991692,"uid":67045,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bf85cd0e20aacef8c84806b776a603d628eb07ed","tid":991692,"uid":229408,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"不斷聽果首當日認識佢而鍾意左既歌<br />\n一播就諗起佢<br />\n單曲循環可以一個月播左百幾次<br />\n每日返工放工都聽<br />\n懷疑緊自己係咪有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"6. 會將身邊發生既所有事，自動與目標對象既回憶（或單方面FF既共同回憶）連結，然後將其放至無限大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de88532491e5198b8b5211507faa76f28cd085ca","tid":991692,"uid":66253,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33d7a89fde6f9a44fa3976710b7defc4ffdeb2a0","tid":991692,"uid":126255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"係同佢個chatroom到打千字文 <br />\n但永遠都唔會有send出去嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885702d32542aaf57d2405c473644dc74fff176e","tid":991692,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"樓豬睇睇醫生好"},{"pid":"12cde1e1d18e1a07df97c6b4bd8f11c227120687","tid":991692,"uid":166538,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b971fb645633da782a8a18dbe3a5aa5680eac90","tid":991692,"uid":37666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":